title: DynLoad (Struct)
text:
TYPE DynLoad : STRUCT
A load that is attached to the end effector.

rows.Name: Inertia
rows.Comment: The inertia of the load defined in the center of mass frame.

rows.Name: CenterOfMassFrame
rows.Comment:
The center of mass frame of the load relative to the machines flange.
[vT.dX] = [vT.dY] = [vT.dZ] = u
